sequenceDiagram
  %% Diagram 73: Vendor Write API Idempotency and Consistency Flow

  autonumber
  actor V as Vendor
  participant API as Vendor Write API (/products,/orders,/campaigns)
  participant Idem as Idempotency Store
  participant Cmd as Command Handler
  participant DB as Write Model
  participant Outbox as Event Outbox/Bus
  participant Audit as Audit/Event Store

  V->>API: Authenticated write request + idempotency key
  API->>Idem: Check idempotency key
  alt Duplicate key
    Idem-->>API: Existing result reference
    API-->>V: Replay-safe prior response
  else New key
    API->>Cmd: Validate domain rules
    alt Validation fails
      Cmd-->>API: Reject, no mutation
      API-->>V: 4xx domain error
    else Validation passes
      Cmd->>DB: Persist mutation transaction
      alt DB commit conflict/failure
        DB-->>Cmd: Conflict or write failure
        Cmd-->>API: Reject, no durable mutation
        API-->>V: 409/5xx controlled response
      else Commit success
        DB-->>Cmd: Commit success
        Cmd->>Outbox: Publish domain event
        Cmd->>Audit: Append audit/event record
        Cmd-->>API: Success payload
        API-->>V: 2xx response
      end
    end
  end
